data.description: Charming Custom Home on 1.4 Acres this delightful 2001 well-kept custom home offers a blend of comfort, privacy, and versatility. Nestled away from the main road, it exudes a cozy ambiance that invites you to unwind. Let’s explore its features: Approx 2700 sq. ft. of well-designed living area awaits you w/3 bdrms & 3 full baths, this home provides ample space for family and guests. A fireplace adds warmth and charm, creating a cozy atmosphere during cooler evenings. Two separate living areas allow flexibility for relaxation and entertaining, The 2-car garage includes a workshop area, perfect for DIY projects or hobbies. An oversized additional covered parking pad ensures convenience & protection for your vehicles. The large, private backyard beckons with endless possibilities. Imagine a chicken coop, a garden area, a firepit where you can gather for cozy evenings under the stars or simply a serene space to unwind and enjoy nature.  With plenty of room, consider building a shop or additional structures.  Let your little ones and furry friends play freely in this spacious setting.  Whether you’re relaxing indoors or tending to your garden this home provides a delightful lifestyle.
